<P><font face="Times New Roman, Times, serif" size="5"><b>On the picket line</b></font><BR>
<font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2">July 12, 2002 | Pages 10 and 11</font></p>

<P><font face="Times New Roman, Times, serif" size="3"> OTHER STORIES BELOW<BR>
